	(text "For 1000Base-T operation, differential data from the media\nis transmitted and received on all four pairs.\nFor 100Base-TX and 10Base-T operation, only MDIAP/N and MDIBP/N are used.\nAuto MDIX can reverse the pairs MDIAP/N and MDIBP/N. Each of the differential pairs has an internal 100-ohm termination resistor"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 80.01 146.05 0)
		(effects
